{"tid":1969733,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"《及x雨財務經理個仔借錢唔還 扼人買口罩  》","createTime":"2020-04-12T15:29:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T01:05:29.000Z","uid":155838,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5d3a43a558111eba751ef6fad4d650c63efd7517","tid":1969733,"uid":155838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T15:29:39.000Z","msg":"《及x雨財務經理個仔孫梓軒借錢唔還 呃市民口罩錢  》<br />\n<br />\n此男孫梓軒，於3月20日因為簽屋租約原因，問我借45,000港元並聲稱第二日佢媽咪過數俾佢之後會過返俾我，但一路拖到4月1日都未理會過我嘅訊息。<br />\n<br />\n其後我喺4月1號晚上門係佢自願嘅情況之下成功簽咗借據（拍住影片佢寫的）並承諾4月4日前還錢，但因為佢字體唔工整我想佢簽多一張，喺呢個時候佢爸爸打嚟之後佢入房聽電話，聽完電話出返嚟態度就180度轉變，唔肯簽任何借據並報警叫警察逼我離開。<br />\n<br />\n呢$45,000係我辛苦嘅血汗錢好唔想咁樣俾人呃咗去，但佢到而家都冇任何還款嘅態度。<br />\n到4月7日因為佢要交屋租更想向其他人想借錢。<br />\n<br />\n因為呢件事令到我生活情緒同健康大受影響。<br />\n<br />\n此外孫子軒喺早前更去泰國同各大市民講會幫大家買口罩，叫大家過數俾佢佢先會幫大家買口罩，但當佢回港之後，並冇履行承諾將口罩派發比購買者。<br />\n<br />\n題外話孫子軒嘅爸爸媽媽係及X雨財務公司嘅經理都係涉嫌商業詐騙案並判罪成。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1235095/即時-香港-涉串謀低價拍賣丁屋案-押至4月判刑\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1235095%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E6%B6%89%E4%B8%B2%E8%AC%80%E4%BD%8E%E5%83%B9%E6%8B%8D%E8%B3%A3%E4%B8%81%E5%B1%8B%E6%A1%88-%E6%8A%BC%E8%87%B34%E6%9C%88%E5%88%A4%E5%88%91&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962ZojzYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=c848ce4c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1235095%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E6%B6%89%E4%B8%B2%E8%AC%80%E4%BD%8E%E5%83%B9%E6%8B%8D%E8%B3%A3%E4%B8%81%E5%B1%8B%E6%A1%88-%E6%8A%BC%E8%87%B34%E6%9C%88%E5%88%A4%E5%88%91&h=9fab6915\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1235095/即時-香港-涉串謀低價拍賣丁屋案-押至4月判刑</a><br />\n<br />\n以下係佢嘅少少資料希望大家廣傳出去<br />\nFacebook:Hin Sth<br />\nIG:6hin6<br />\n電話：9025 6665<br />\n希望大家幫我討回公道<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nr8E7RT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNr8E7RT.png&h=ca742fa2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FRaW95f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFRaW95f.png&h=fc38ef28&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3EmZ7R3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3EmZ7R3.png&h=ae13b378&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KEXOgLs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKEXOgLs.png&h=d085ead0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/12/232904_42557ac66cc6c175d10a21360767547e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F12%2F232904_42557ac66cc6c175d10a21360767547e.png&h=c3c68869&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/12/232905_3f82e9dd8e71e6052fbbb49b2209dac8.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F12%2F232905_3f82e9dd8e71e6052fbbb49b2209dac8.jpeg&h=cf3c1dcd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/12/232906_6b7840b856546cafca43e33f23b21256.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F12%2F232906_6b7840b856546cafca43e33f23b21256.jpeg&h=19e76e7f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/12/232906_0c9e9aeb4ff05860be07af2d46a5338e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F12%2F232906_0c9e9aeb4ff05860be07af2d46a5338e.png&h=a4f1e849&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"348f01e614521b24d622dbcb964e85832b426e1b","tid":1969733,"uid":155838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d3a43a558111eba751ef6fad4d650c63efd7517","tid":1969733,"uid":155838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T15:29:39.000Z","msg":"《及x雨財務經理個仔孫梓軒借錢唔還 呃市民口罩錢  》<br />\n<br />\n此男孫梓軒，於3月20日因為簽屋租約原因，問我借45